ENDPOINT: listSpecies, karyotype, chromosomeLength, geneSeq, geneInfo, geneCalc, geneList

ESEMBL REST API ENDPOINTS:

        server = "http://rest.ensembl.org"

        for list species = "/info/species?"
        for karyotype = "/info/assembly/{}?".format(msg_split[1]) where msg_split[1] is the specie
        for chromo length = /info/assembly/{}?".format(msg_split2[1]) where the variable is the input introduce (chromosome of a specie)
        for gene sequence = /lookup/symbol/homo_sapiens/{}?".format(msg_split[1]) where msg_split[1] is the gene
        for gene info = "/lookup/symbol/homo_sapiens/{}?".format(msg_split[1]) where msg_split[1] is the gene
        for gene calculation = /lookup/symbol/homo_sapiens/{}?".format(msg_split[1]) where msg_split[1] is the gene
        for gene list = /overlap/region/human/" + str(msg_split2[1]) + ":" + msg_split2[3] + "-" + msg_split2[
                        5] + "?feature=gene"  where the variables are the 3 inputs introduced (end, start and gene)
